    "description": "通过免费入门版：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽享刺激竞速动作体验</h2>无论面对何种赛道材质——沥青、沙土、草甸、木制、塑料、冰面甚至水下场景，你都得精准掌控车速与漂移，从容应对飞跃、回环、贴墙过弯与急转挑战。<br>精进车技，驾驭赛道，获得胜利！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/d1f18a751fc4b0960343d75357459e07.poster.avif?t=1769529679\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/d1f18a751fc4b0960343d75357459e07.webm?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/d1f18a751fc4b0960343d75357459e07.mp4?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在玩家自制的顶级赛道上竞速</h2>每周，你都能在五个场景之一，挑战五条全新的短道赛：Red Island、Blue Bay、Green Coast、White Shore 和标志性的体育馆。<br>每个赛季中，你都能探索官方赛事中最易上手的赛道。<br>在每小时更新的街机频道，体验玩家自制的最具创意的赛道。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/b03da7249c89e18859154c87baed73b0.poster.avif?t=1769529679\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/b03da7249c89e18859154c87baed73b0.webm?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/b03da7249c89e18859154c87baed73b0.mp4?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收藏声望载具皮肤</h2>攀登全球与地区排行榜，收集奖牌和奖杯。你将凭借精湛的车技与游戏内成就，解锁《赛道狂飙》声望最高的载具皮肤，并以独特的方式秀出你的非凡实力！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/a791fdf8e584d16d50a4ff12c56677fe.poster.avif?t=1769529679\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/a791fdf8e584d16d50a4ff12c56677fe.webm?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/a791fdf8e584d16d50a4ff12c56677fe.mp4?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >表达你的创意</h2>利用赛道编辑器（简易版与进阶版）及 3000 余种构件模块和道具，打造自定义赛道。使用皮肤编辑器设计你自己的载具皮肤，通过回放编辑器记录并分享高光赛事的精彩影像。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/ef5ddb5676f2bd978caf4fab318f2bda.poster.avif?t=1769529679\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/ef5ddb5676f2bd978caf4fab318f2bda.webm?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225070/extras/ef5ddb5676f2bd978caf4fab318f2bda.mp4?t=1769529679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过为期 1 年的俱乐部版：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁《赛道狂飙》的无限世界</h2>你将尽享完整赛季征程、顶尖社区创作、专属活动与高级载具皮肤。开设自己的线上房间，创作赛道与游戏活动，并邀请全体玩家一起竞速！",
